;  [[SQLITE_SCANSTAT_EXPLAIN]] <dt>SQLITE_SCANSTAT_EXPLAIN</dt>
;  <dd>^The "const char *" variable pointed to by the T parameter will be set
;  to a zero-terminated UTF-8 string containing the [EXPLAIN QUERY PLAN]
